@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mbanfy(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.sin((tmp + 0.50 * v0 + 0.12)))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.abs(v1 + 0.26) - (v1 + 0.88 / tmp + 0.25)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.59)))
    v2 = 0.34
    tmp = tmp
    v2 = wp.abs((0.14 + v2))
    data[tid] = v0
